<h3>1.2 images:</h3>
<p>HTML images are defined with the "<img>" tag &it consists of following attributes:<br> source file (src) | alt text (alt) | width | height </p>
<p>The "src" could contain:<br>1. Absolute URL (domain name of the image file; hosted on another webpage/server" OR <br>2.Relative URL (acutal file; local to this webpage) </p>
<img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQcCoQdWVWE10Vb2MrIafIFaNqBO7iX6afet3hu6PezwtAQuH_ceVS9jSv7_5a1tWGu80o&usqp=CAU" alt="" width="142" height="150">
